# .yamlover/body.yamlover — the served root's instance overlay (merged over the directory).
#
# The yamlover SELF-IMPORT (IMPORTS.md §4), written EXPLICITLY here for documentation. Every
# project implicitly imports the yamlover project under the alias `yamlover`; this line just makes
# that implicit key visible. When THIS project is the served root the engine DE-MATERIALIZES the
# key (the taxonomy is already real at `:$defs` / `:tags`, so `::yamlover:X` ≡ `::X`); in any other
# project the same key resolves to the bundled yamlover taxonomy. Omitting this line changes
# nothing — the engine injects it when absent.
yamlover: *::: yamlover.inthemoon.net
